    "body": "The only other mention of `hasSpecialOffer` is in the current refinements widget\n\n``` javascript\nthis.instantsearch.addWidget(\n    instantsearch.widgets.currentRefinedValues({\n        container: '#journeys-current-refined-widget',\n        clearAll: 'after',\n        attributes: [\n            {\n                name: 'price',\n                label: '',\n                transformData: function(item) {\n                    item.name = accounting.formatMoney(item.name);\n                    return item;\n                },\n                template: '{{#operator}}{{{displayOperator}}} {{/operator}} {{name}}'\n            },\n            {\n                name: 'hasSpecialOffer',\n                label: 'Specials',\n                template: '{{label}}',\n            },\n            {\n                name: 'numberOfDays',\n                label: 'days',\n                template: '{{#operator}}{{{displayOperator}}} {{/operator}} {{name}} {{label}}'\n            },\n        ],\n        templates: {\n            header: 'Current Filters'\n        },\n    })\n);\n```\n\nI can provide the staging URL if that is any help?\n",
